ssets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連狗： 和理非<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />腦魔： 記者？<br />\n<br />\n其實一開始可以畫d易入口d, 好似老夫子咁深入淺出容易吸引d深黃淺藍 （深黃跟本唔洗睇佢都明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），又容易translate做其他語言，例如：<br />\n<br />\n1.為所欲為Tee ( 講腦魔教連狗著為所欲為tee，然後比連豬整蠱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 連豬病都冇得帶口罩，變咗豬流感<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.或者用連豬連狗將一d好人好事，黃絲小店分享比大家，例如全民幫黃店清潔同say sorry（或者講下咩店唔幫襯得）<br />\n<br />\n大家幫手推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164ae9a93307de057a8c758cd01b1dda7a48d8a1","tid":1637091,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:49:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccff3693d8f0f3459ab280e9e33603a2b4b5ca37","tid":1637091,"uid":124410,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:50:22.000Z","msg":"配合政府玩鳩港豬<br />\n等你班人仲堅持唔割吖嗱"},{"pid":"8552925182f8cfda7772d143fd119a496b5e6f8f","tid":1637091,"uid":163819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:51:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}